# Restaurant Images
Store all restaurant and food menu images here.

Suggested organization:
- food/ (food items, dishes)
- interior/ (restaurant interior photos)
- exterior/ (building exterior)
- staff/ (team photos)
- events/ (special events, celebrations)

Image guidelines:
- Format: JPG or PNG
- Resolution: 1920x1080px for hero images, 800x600px for gallery
- File size: Under 500KB each for fast loading
- Use descriptive filenames (e.g., grilled-chicken-special.jpg)